    <repository>
      <id>apache-pekko-snapshots</id>
      <url>https://repository.apache.org/content/groups/snapshots</url>
      <layout>default</layout>
      <snapshots>
        <enabled>true</enabled>
      </snapshots>
    </repository>
  </repositories> Define the library dependencies with the 
